room_title: Escape room "Trapped in the 80s" by Escape Rooms by Franknicky in Sandusky
review: Such attention to detail, and truly immersive experience. Got a chance to chat with Spencer whose raw ingenuity and knack for the creative was apparent... this is a guy who loves what he does and whose work is a testament to that! We did the 80's themed room and had a blast with our bridal party!

room_title: Escape room "Trapped in the 80s" by Escape Rooms by Franknicky in Sandusky
review: This was sooooo much fun! We beat Unlock the 80’s and can’t wait to try more of the Franknicky Escape Rooms. 100% give this place

room_title: Escape room "Trapped in the 80s" by Escape Rooms by Franknicky in Sandusky
